ist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-02-800x1071.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-02-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-02-1148x1536.jpg 1148w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-02-1530x2048.jpg 1530w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1913px) 100vw, 1913px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe house is conceived as a living element in the landscape, with gentle curves and fluid lines that adapt to the terrain and merge with the surrounding vegetation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2368\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-03.jpg\" alt=\"A modern home with a green roof also features a material palette of concrete and wood.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-03-940x1159.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-03-800x987.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-03-768x947.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-03-1245x1536.jpg 1245w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-03-1661x2048.jpg 1661w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe three-level garden extends from the ground to the rooftop, culminating in an overlook facing the polo field. It integrates vegetation organically and breaks conventional boundaries between interior and exterior, up and down.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-04.jpg\" alt=\"A modern home with a green roof also features a material palette of concrete and wood.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-04.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-04-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-04-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-04-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-04-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eMaterials such as concrete and wood are chosen based on their ability to age gracefully and withstand the elements, ensuring a lasting and sustainable integration with the environment.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-05.jpg\" alt=\"A modern home with a green roof also features a material palette of concrete and wood.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-05.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-05-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof-201124-812-05-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/modern-house-with-green-roof